媒体给了《漆黑的黎明》较好的评价，游戏在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的汇总得分分别为79%<ref name="mc" />和80%<ref name="gr" />。但评论对本作的评价则普遍不如Game Boy Advance上的前两作：首作《[[黄金太阳_开启的封印|开启的封印]]》在Metacritic和GameRankings的汇总得分为91%<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun?q=Golden%20Sun | title=''Golden Sun'' (2001-GBA) | publisher=Metacritic | accessdate=2008-01-20 | language=en | archive-date=2008-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209190929/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun?q=Golden%20Sun | dead-url=no }}</ref>和90%<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/468548.asp?q=golden%20sun | title=''Golden Sun'' at GR | publisher=GameRankings | accessdate=2008-01-20 | language=en | archive-date=2012-09-15 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ahb84hJX?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/468548-golden-sun/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，第二作《[[黄金太阳_失落的时代|失落的时代]]》则为86%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wireless.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensunthelostage |title=''Golden Sun: The Lost Age'' (2003-GBA) |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2008-01-20 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714074745/http://wireless.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensunthelostage |archivedate=2011-07-14 }}</ref>和87%<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/561356.asp | title=''Golden Sun: The Lost Age'' at GR | publisher=GameRankings | accessdate=2008-01-20 | language=en | archive-date=2012-10-05 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVv3znt?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/561356-golden-sun-the-lost-age/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。<!-- [[Gamezone|Gamezone]]评论游戏道“虽然远不如黄金太阳首作巧妙，但对他们在任天堂DS平台上，将系列制作为3D画面的努力，任天堂应该赞扬”<ref>{{cite web| author=GameZone Staff | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Review | url=http://nds.gamezone.com/products/golden-sun-dark-dawn-nds/reviews/golden_sun_dark_dawn | publisher=GameZone | accessdate=2012-05-19 | language=en | date=2011-01-03}}</ref>。 -->英国杂志《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》评价道“虽然缺乏影响力，但黄金太阳系列仍有很多话题”<ref name="edge" />。

游戏的画面和精灵系统受到了广泛的好评。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]评论道“游戏从GBA的2D世界进入了DS的全3D，视觉效果良好。游戏精神力、精灵行动和召唤的电影般画效都棒极了。”<ref name="gamespot" />而[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]则称战斗画面“尤为令人眼前一亮，但却不会感到华而不实或令人厌倦”<ref name="1up" />。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]称赞了游戏独特的精灵系统“使资深RPG玩家也不会感到游戏无聊”<ref name="gamesradar" />，而IGN也称“玩家可以召唤巨人或神兽来协助战斗，每次召唤都有过场动画。那非常酷。”<ref name="ign" />[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]称赞了游戏的解谜设置，并评论道“《漆黑的黎明》的迷宫就像其前作一样几乎很难，但你拿到难以触及奖赏后的满足感，就如探索者破解了谜团一般<ref name="gamerevolution">{{cite web| author=Josh Laddin | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Review | url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/golden-sun-ds | publisher=GameRevolution.com | accessdate=2012-05-01 | language=en | date=2010-11-30}}</ref>。《漆黑的黎明》可以通过辞典让不熟悉前作的人上手<ref name="gametrailers">{{cite web| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Review | url=http://www.gametrailers.com/gamereview.php?id=11421 | publisher=GameTrailers.com | accessdate=2012-05-01 | language=en}}</ref>，游戏博客[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]评论道“如果遇到你不熟悉的词汇、概念或人物，只需使用触摸笔轻点击一下，定义就可弹出。这是对新手是非常友好的。”<ref name="kotaku">{{cite web| author=Mike Fahey | title=Review: Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Relives The Glory Days | url=http://kotaku.com/5697770/review-golden-sun-dark-dawn-relives-the-glory-days | publisher=kotaku.com | accessdate=2012-05-01 | language=en | date=2010-10-29}}</ref>

对游戏的批评则集中在简单的战斗以及如同前作的冗长的对话上。许多评论认为游戏的战斗简单<ref name="gameinformer" /><ref>{{cite web | author=Jeremy Parish | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Review | url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/golden-sun-dark-dawn-review?pager.offset=1 | publisher=1up | accessdate=2012-04-20 | language=en | date=2010-11-26 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411053913/http://www.1up.com/reviews/golden-sun-dark-dawn-review?pager.offset=1 | archivedate=2015-04-11 }}</ref>，Game Revolution评价战斗“可以用精灵猛砸敌人来代替武器攻击”<ref name="gamerevolution" />，而GamesRadar也批评道“不仅己方的战斗容易，而且精神力补给还很快，你可以自由的用来治疗或攻击，而不必单只使用的道具——你从不会发现资源匮乏，或感到自己陷入困境”<ref name="gamesradar" />。而游戏依然延续了前作对话啰嗦的毛病<ref name="eurogamer" /><ref name="ign" /><ref name="nintendoworldreport">{{cite web| author=James Jones | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/review/24506 | publisher=Nintendo World Report | accessdate=2012-04-19 | language=en | date=2010-12-03}}</ref>，1UP.com评论道“游戏的主角和反派有种不可思议的技巧，能把他们真正想传达的极其简单的事情重复说上三四遍”<ref name="1up" />。游戏新增了表情反馈功能，可以让沉默的主角回应其他角色，但有评论认为该功能是多余的，因为其并不能影响剧情<ref name="gameinformer" /><ref name="gametrailers" />。此外[[Nintendo_World_Report|Nintendo World Report]]认为《漆黑的黎明》的音效和GBA平台上的前作相似，但却不像前作那么令人留恋<ref name="nintendoworldreport" />，而[[RPGFan|RPGFan]]也称游戏的音乐“多种多样，但往往会淡入背景中，并很快被人遗忘”<ref>{{cite web| author=Andrew Barker | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn | url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/Golden_Sun_DS/index.html | publisher=RPGFan | accessdate=2012-04-17 | language=en | date=2011-01-28}}</ref>。<!-- [[Thunderbolt|Thunderbolt]]则称迷宫会让老玩家感到打了折扣，“一些迷宫不消几分钟就可完成”，且“简短的迷宫没有充分发挥它的潜力”<ref>{{cite web| author=Justin Boot | title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn | url=http://www.thunderboltgames.com/reviews/article/golden-sun-dark-dawn-review-for-ds.html | publisher=Thunderbolt | accessdate=2012-04-17 | language=en | date=2010-12-16}}</ref>。 -->

